    {
      "id": "1308079818166907",
      "score": 4,
      "review_title": "Not bad, but it needs more!",
      "review_description": "For what it’s worth, this is pretty fun. The physics are actually surprisingly good, online works fine, there’s a decent selection of things for you to drive and maps to play. It even lets you drive high speed!\n\nHowever though, that’s kinda all it’s got. With driving, the sounds are kinda annoying, and the physics are missing some things. We should have some momentum changes, like allowing us to tilt the bike for sharper turns, air physics so that we can do tricks, and allow for things like loops. That would make the ramps and whatnot more fun.\n\nAnd the handling is kinda bad for certain things. The quad is totally goofy and the fast bike just flips around sometimes?  We need more ground control.\n\nAlso there’s like no racing functionality? We should at least be able to record and playback things we do.",
      "date": 1780696409,
      "review_helpful_count": 0,
      "author_display_name": "FLAME83",
      "author_alias": "FLAME83",
      "developer_response": null
    },
